      "content": "i know i should talk to someone, but even that feels exhausting. like, what am i even going to say? \"hey, i destroyed my family's future and i don't want to live with the embarrassment\"? it feels like everyone's just waiting for me to crawl into a hole. i just keep thinking that if i wasn't here, the shame would just... go away. at least they wouldn't have to look at me.",
